Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.68,0:21:52.10,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}純真さが シンプルな力に 変わる 世界に影をつくりだす
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.75,0:22:06.64,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}ガラスケ一スに横たわる 光の存在に触れたくても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.72,0:22:13.74,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}振り上げた手 降ろせなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.11,0:22:22.41,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}落ちるようにしゃがみこんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.54,0:22:30.73,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}Prototype boy 明日の理想だけで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.97,0:22:38.22,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}語り継ぐような 美談にもならないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.43,0:22:45.55,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}この体を失いそうな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.75,0:22:54.72,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}ギリギリの場所が 哀しいくらい似合ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.68,0:21:52.10,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}當純真變為單純的力量 世界由此誕生了影子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.75,0:22:06.64,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}穿透過玻璃櫥 感觸著這光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.72,0:22:13.74,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}舉起的手無法放下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.11,0:22:22.41,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}卻如同墜落般跌下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.54,0:22:30.73,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}Prototype boy 拋開明天的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.97,0:22:38.22,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}即便無法成為傳承的美談
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.43,0:22:45.55,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}如同就要失去這副身軀一般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.75,0:22:54.72,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}在極限的邊緣 跌入悲傷的深淵
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.69,0:00:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,測試體E-57 腦量子波手術完成
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.92,0:00:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入術後觀察過程
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.54,0:00:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人嗎 有人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.25,0:00:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人能聽到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.74,0:00:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦袋裡有聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.59,0:00:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.77,0:00:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.70,0:00:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.11,0:00:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人能聽到我的聲音嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.14,0:01:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你在和我說話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.58,0:01:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能聽到我聲音嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.84,0:01:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡 你在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.84,0:01:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是就在你面前嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.07,0:01:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.87,0:01:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 能和人說上話真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.76,0:01:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我一直都是孤單一人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.21,0:01:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很感謝你能來到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.01,0:01:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.06,0:01:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.49,0:01:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.16,0:01:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.17,0:01:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 我想不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.57,0:01:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.27,0:01:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.72,0:01:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連名字也想不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.53,0:01:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我來給你取個名字好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.46,0:01:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想 你的名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.43,0:01:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就叫阿雷魯亞好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.00,0:01:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷魯亞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.71,0:01:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是感謝神的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.83,0:02:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝 感謝什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.34,0:02:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還用說嗎 當然是活著這件事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.09,0:02:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毋庸置疑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是對我的洗禮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.45,0:03:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.07,0:03:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有5年前阻止了阿扎帝斯坦的內亂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.69,0:04:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對此我表示萬分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不進行戰鬥而阻止了內亂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.42,0:04:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為這種行為是非常可貴的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些事就不提了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.87,0:04:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今後有什麼打算
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.33,0:04:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,返回阿扎帝斯坦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.94,0:04:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太胡鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.33,0:04:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保安局會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.72,0:04:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據你的說法 很可能聯邦也介入了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.16,0:04:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有加入聯邦的阿扎帝斯坦被世界所拋棄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經濟崩潰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.85,0:04:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為指導者拉瑟的去世
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保守派和改革派陷入戰爭的泥潭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.98,0:04:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 正因為如此 我才要…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.85,0:04:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 托勒密向阿扎帝斯坦航行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.63,0:04:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.00,0:04:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.80,0:04:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去艦橋了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.38,0:04:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我冒昧的問一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.33,0:04:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是情侶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.26,0:04:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是\N不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女的直覺錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪小姐如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.02,0:05:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是沒有重新穿上制服的意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.69,0:05:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅 命中率如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.85,0:05:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,78% 78%
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.48,0:05:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不能像哥哥那樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.37,0:05:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.08,0:05:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是叫菲露特吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經常能感覺到你的視線呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.98,0:05:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.68,0:05:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特喜歡洛克昂 菲露特喜歡洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.84,0:05:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.31,0:05:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.10,0:06:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不在乎這些的話 要和我交往嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.62,0:06:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有這個意思的話 之後來我的房間…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.80,0:06:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被甩了 被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.70,0:06:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.26,0:06:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被比來比去的 誰受得了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能陪我喝一杯麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.76,0:06:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a}阿拉伯海 海上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.57,0:06:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俘虜的Gundam機師被劫走 而且KATARON的人也被救走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是失態啊 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.33,0:06:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為錯誤的估計了天行者的戰力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.16,0:06:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不聽解釋 A-LAWS不需要無能的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林特少佐 下次的作戰由閣下來負責
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.47,0:07:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我來教教您A-LAWS的戰鬥方法吧 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.29,0:07:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請一定讓我學習一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.16,0:07:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.01,0:07:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅長掃蕩戰的阿爾巴·林特少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.31,0:07:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然把那個臭名昭著的男人招來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.49,0:07:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據保安局的證言 Gundam好像把關押中的阿扎帝斯坦皇女帶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.73,0:07:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閣下怎麼看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.56,0:07:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說Gundam機師裡有中東出身的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.36,0:07:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算為了年輕的公主殿下去當白馬王子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.67,0:07:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我推測現在天行者正在為私情而行動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.85,0:07:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫助作為機師的夥伴就是最好的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.63,0:07:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這附近張網以待應該是最好的選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.22,0:07:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 允許你使用Trilobite
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝 還有件事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.44,0:08:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本次作戰希望也能讓他參加
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr.武士道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.44,0:08:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅不到5分鐘的閃電戰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.46,0:08:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦船沉入海中 激發海嘯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受此影響 部隊陷入混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.66,0:08:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周圍濕度上升 導致粒子武器的效力減半
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.13,0:08:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有四架Gundam的合作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.65,0:08:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大膽與細緻共存的戰術
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.26,0:08:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡看到過…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.71,0:08:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trilobite準備出發 Trilobite準備出發
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.51,0:08:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trilobite？ 資料中的新型機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.37,0:08:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然開發了搭載GN DRIVE的MA
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.50,0:08:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說是有位女性捐贈了巨額的資金
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.02,0:09:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好事者真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對第四小隊下達了降落地面的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.74,0:09:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈勒維准尉 請立刻到艦橋來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.04,0:09:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.67,0:09:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS隊準備出發
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.71,0:09:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到了G1傳來的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.86,0:09:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子 果然是朝阿扎帝斯坦而去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.61,0:09:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要這麼做嗎 克勞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.74,0:09:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我們的目的而言 天行者是不可缺少的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 幫助他們的話也可以保護瑪麗娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.27,0:09:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.56,0:09:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要幫助她 你重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.44,0:09:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.62,0:09:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說要離開王宮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.38,0:09:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下 就現在聯邦政府的政策而言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.05,0:09:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這個國家加入聯邦 也沒有未來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:10:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我要用我自己的方法來創造這個國家的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿扎帝斯坦不能採用的你的方法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.89,0:10:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅是讓這個國家站起來是沒有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.33,0:10:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞斯 讓我也和部隊一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.56,0:10:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.19,0:10:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會拖後腿的 拜託了 克勞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該有我能做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那 要不要和我一起來 到阿扎帝斯坦來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.08,0:10:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想建立一個沒有紛爭 大家都能正常生活的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.14,0:10:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.33,0:10:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所能做的只有戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.61,0:10:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說這麼悲傷的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那 戰爭不會孕育任何東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.42,0:11:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在進入天行者之前 我也是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 確實有自破壞之中誕生的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.50,0:11:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了未來 世界的扭曲就由Gundam來糾正
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.42,0:11:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我和Gundam一起戰鬥的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深度 固定在3200
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…沒關係麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.07,0:11:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看到這種機密
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.61,0:11:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人手不足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.56,0:11:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是有宇宙技師的二級執照麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.25,0:11:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說了 不勞動就沒飯吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.70,0:11:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.30,0:11:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我伊恩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊恩·維斯迪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.72,0:12:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊恩先生 你為何會來到此處呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.37,0:12:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對戰爭深惡痛絕 希望能根絕之
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.93,0:12:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡每個人都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.10,0:12:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有被送到最前線戰鬥之人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.98,0:12:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被軍隊進行了肉體改造之人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.49,0:12:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被恐怖襲擊奪去親屬之人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.02,0:12:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被游擊隊培養成長之人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.83,0:12:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在戰爭中失去了最重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.10,0:12:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界就是這麼現實的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.15,0:12:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我們就是罪犯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.40,0:12:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總會遭到報應的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.79,0:12:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在戰爭被根絕之後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.76,0:12:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索瑪·皮瑞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得 是人革聯的超兵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.17,0:12:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼之前沒發覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.00,0:12:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能介入我的腦量子波的 只有瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.22,0:12:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被國聯軍抓到的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:13:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感覺是到了償還罪孽的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.61,0:13:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至覺得就那樣腐朽風化掉也好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.91,0:13:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 現在不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.54,0:13:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想把瑪麗找回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方是敵人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.20,0:13:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.61,0:13:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你 已經把超人機關的設施給…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.60,0:13:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把自己的同胞們殺掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗如果知道這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.23,0:13:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會恨我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做的 就是這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 就算是會被憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.74,0:13:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人羨慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.05,0:13:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.49,0:13:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經 找到戰鬥的理由了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.68,0:13:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的戰鬥之中 有那樣的理由麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.84,0:13:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是贊同了伊奧利亞的計劃才參加進來的麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.86,0:13:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.63,0:13:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時想著要消除戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.73,0:13:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 除了那一點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時的我還想要把自己不祥的過去抹殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.12,0:14:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不祥的過去…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.26,0:14:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是抱著這樣的想法戰鬥的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.54,0:14:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.77,0:14:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為了堅持自我 讓很多的生命就那麼犧牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.79,0:14:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.99,0:14:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我抹殺不掉過去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.69,0:14:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對現在的我來說 已經沒有戰鬥的理由了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.33,0:14:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在這裡的理由也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.24,0:14:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有留在這裡的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.39,0:14:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這麼覺得的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.48,0:14:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種安慰…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 為什麼你會救了我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥的理由 一定能找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.59,0:14:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是你的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.11,0:14:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arios Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios的後繼機體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.05,0:14:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用這架機體 就用Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.66,0:14:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會把瑪麗找回來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.94,0:14:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算哈雷魯亞已經不在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.62,0:14:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦量子波不能再用也好…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.63,0:14:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥的理由麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.03,0:14:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去的我會否定這個概念吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.88,0:15:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂  克麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.07,0:15:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡希特 莫雷諾先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.33,0:15:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還能夠再來一次麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.28,0:15:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站在整個世界的對面…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.04,0:15:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 守護自己重要的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.32,0:15:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米裡奧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.75,0:15:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密號 馬上要穿過霍爾木茲海峽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.04,0:15:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…這周圍太安靜了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.04,0:15:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魚群的樣子也有點… 在這個深度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.01,0:15:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.60,0:15:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E聲納出現反應
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.84,0:15:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6個敵目標正高速接近中的說!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是魚雷!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.74,0:15:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.67,0:15:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN力場 最大展開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.07,0:15:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.60,0:15:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵襲!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.06,0:15:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在魚雷裡有重化合物…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.18,0:15:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲納被無效化了的說!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.04,0:15:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有能在這個深度活動的敵人?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.43,0:15:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型機!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.00,0:16:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在計劃地點拖住敵艦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.58,0:16:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要入虎穴奪子了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.17,0:16:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去艦艇中央部分!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.95,0:16:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.21,0:16:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第2波 要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.49,0:16:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大型魚雷兩發!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.51,0:16:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN力場 被突破了的說!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.42,0:16:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新武器麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.45,0:16:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下部莢艙進水!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.60,0:16:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算要Gundam出擊 這種深度下也…!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要讓托勒密號浮上了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到Gundam能承受的深度!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.89,0:16:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從海上來的爆雷…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.93,0:16:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可能在使用的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.83,0:16:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化學爆彈!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.45,0:16:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2分鐘的爆破之後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用Trilobite進行接近戰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.84,0:16:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法拜見敵艦被壓碎的情景倒是有點可惜…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.71,0:16:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林特少佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.15,0:17:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索敵到前期行動為止都很出色
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.24,0:17:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 對方的指揮官會出什麼招呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.95,0:17:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船體被覆蓋上樹脂 炮門無法打開!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.99,0:17:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舵也不行了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.20,0:17:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 敵人在哪!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.03,0:17:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E聲納 不能使用的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒什麼對策麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.36,0:17:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.31,0:17:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對策是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.46,0:17:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪小姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.68,0:17:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上爆雷就會停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.00,0:17:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著 海裡的敵人正在向這裡接近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.92,0:17:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備直接攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人 突擊艦體左舷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.18,0:17:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,損 損害很大!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.41,0:17:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去 被壓壞的危險也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真夠幸運的 我們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.43,0:17:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到的敵人就在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密號已經到了Gundam可以出擊的深度
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:18:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且敵人連下部莢艙的注水時間都替我們省了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.74,0:18:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比MS的推力的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.59,0:18:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這部Trilobite才不會…!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.21,0:18:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊還有王牌 TRANS-AM!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.31,0:18:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟 竟然會!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.54,0:18:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算在水中 有這麼接近的話…!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.54,0:18:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉開距離 用魚雷!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.77,0:18:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OO 將目標…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.06,0:18:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不和我一起來麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.09,0:18:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去阿扎帝斯坦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.69,0:18:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…將目標
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.12,0:18:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅逐!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.22,0:19:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不可能!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.56,0:19:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trilobite竟然!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.70,0:19:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那 要衝出海面了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.86,0:19:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.52,0:19:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.75,0:19:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是… 是Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.76,0:19:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說 Trilobite已經…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.61,0:19:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓本艦後退
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.07,0:19:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓MS隊出擊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.22,0:19:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經太晚了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架Ahead是!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.26,0:19:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr.武士道!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.13,0:19:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS的新型機!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.19,0:19:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種動作!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.36,0:19:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…麻煩的傢伙麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.68,0:19:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份劍術…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.56,0:20:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會錯 就是那個時候的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.93,0:20:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何等僥倖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.65,0:20:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍辱苟活下來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也終於有價值了!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架機體 測試體E-57!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.79,0:20:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是機體的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的能力…!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.60,0:20:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.74,0:20:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墜落吧 Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.48,0:20:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.77,0:20:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是 KATARON?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.07,0:20:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.66,0:20:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反政府組織麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.64,0:20:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擋我的道!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.25,0:20:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退 重整陣勢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.78,0:20:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.80,0:20:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉… 拒絕和我交手麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.69,0:21:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的領教到了不少哦 少佐閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.96,0:21:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反政府組織KATARON
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.64,0:21:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有如此的戰力…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.08,0:21:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會是誰呢? 想要見我的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.85,0:21:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了呢 瑪麗娜·伊斯瑪依露
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.61,0:21:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 詩琳…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩琳·帕索提婭…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.00,0:21:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.44,0:21:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在是KATARON的成員
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.05,0:21:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個對地球聯邦的行徑高喊反調的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.00,0:23:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於下定決心了麼 比利
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.15,0:23:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來還望多多照顧 叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.60,0:23:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡要稱呼我司令
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.07,0:23:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任命你 繼承已故的列夫曼教授的事業
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.14,0:23:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擔任新型MS的開發主任
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.95,0:23:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,領命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.09,0:23:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.23,0:23:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.32,0:23:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小不合適 好緊…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.94,0:23:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 馬上去再準備一件
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.85,0:23:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我說這樣才好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.84,0:23:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是性騷擾的說 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.02,0:23:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪·李·諾莉艾卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.27,0:23:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久篠…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.33,0:23:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從很久以前開始 就一直在利用我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.83,0:23:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後又踐踏了…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.10,0:23:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的那份心意
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.38,0:24:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被A-LAWS近乎毫無慈悲的攻擊左右的機師
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.53,0:24:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後剎那在紅蓮之炎中 將品味如戲的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.12,0:24:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 故國炎上
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.57,0:24:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份再會 如同一劑猛藥麼


